ent-ClothingNeckBronzeCentcommMedal = Bronze Medal «For Merit to the General Staff»
    .desc = An award presented for diligent service, discipline, and commendable performance of duties in the interests of the General Staff.
ent-ClothingNeckSilverCentcommMedal = Silver Medal «For Special Merit to the General Staff»
    .desc = An award conferred for significant contribution to the activities of the General Staff, exemplary service, and demonstrated initiative in the line of duty.
ent-ClothingNeckGoldCentcommMedal = Gold Medal «For Outstanding Merit to the General Staff»
    .desc = The highest departmental award, presented for exceptional devotion to duty, outstanding leadership, and special merits before the General Staff.
ent-ClothingNeckPlatinumCentcommMedal = Platinum Medal «For Exceptional Merit to the General Staff»
    .desc = A particularly honorable highest award of the General Staff, presented for exceptional contribution, outstanding leadership, and merits that have had a significant impact on the activities and interests of the General Staff.
